CHUNGHWA PICTURE April Sales Fall 13.34% (Table) : 2475 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-05-09T08:12:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-09/chunghwa-picture-april-sales-fall-13-34-table-2475-tt.html
CHUNGHWA PICTURE said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 13.34% to NT$5,538,227,000 from NT$6,390,427,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales           5,538,227        6,390,427   
YOY%             -13.34%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           20,384,304       25,281,757  
YOY%             -19.37% 
=================================================================
 